<article id="node-17048">
<h1 >3.4.8 RAFS - Qualification &amp; Payability</h1>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> THIS SCHEME CLOSED on 31 July 2001 and the following INFORMATION is FOR HISTORICAL PURPOSES ONLY.</p>
<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>This section explains the qualification and payability provisions for <a href="../guide-social-security-law/acronyms#rafs" title="Retirement assistance for farmers scheme">RAFS</a>.</p>
<div class="reference">
<p><strong>Policy reference:</strong> SS Guide <a href="../guide-social-security-law/1/2/3/80">1.2.3.80</a> Retirement Assistance for Farmers Scheme (RAFS) - Description</p>
</div>
</article>	<h2>In this section</h2>
